Program: Omnibus
Title: Nehru
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jq2
Last Broadcast Date: 13 November 1989
Documentary about Jawaharlal Nehru, Indian politician and the first prime minister of India. The programme traces his political beliefs and speaks to those who knew him including his sister Vijaya Lakshmi. Picture: Jawaharlal Nehru, Credit: Getty Images